Getting Help¶

PMHC MDS Helpdesk¶

Strategic Data offers a dedicated Helpdesk which is available to support Primary Health Networks and Provider Organisations implementing NSPT in relation to the PMHC minimum dataset system (MDS).

All MDS enquiries should be directed to support@pmhc-mds.com.
